OL,3,CStamps showcase some of UK's most
OL,4,Cstriking waterfalls
OL,6,FRoyal Mail has unveiled images of 10
OL,7,Fstamps that showcase some of the UK's
OL,8,Fmost spectacular waterfalls.
OL,10,FThe stamps feature photography of
OL,11,Fwaterfalls across the UK, which Royal
OL,12,FMail says captures the power and
OL,13,Fbeauty of some of the country's most
OL,14,Fdramatic natural landscapes.
OL,16,FThe waterfalls shown on the stamps
OL,17,Fare: Rogie Falls; Pollnagollum Cave;
OL,18,FAysgarth Falls; Pistyll Rhaeadr; Becky
OL,19,FFalls; Hardraw Force; Rhaeadr y Graig
OL,20,FLwyd/Conwy Falls; Fairy Pools of Glen
OL,21,FBrittle; High Force; and Ess-na-Larach.
