OL,3,CStamps showcase some of UK's most
OL,4,Cstriking waterfalls
OL,6,FDavid Gold, Royal Mail's director of
OL,7,Fexternal affairs and policy, said:
OL,8,F"The British Isles are rich in natural
OL,9,Fbeauty and these stamps highlight some
OL,10,Fof the UK's most striking waterfalls
OL,11,Fin all four nations.
OL,13,F"They showcase the richness of our
OL,14,Fnatural environment which has been
OL,15,Fshaped by water over thousands of
OL,16,Fyears."
OL,18,FThe stamps, and a range of collectible
OL,19,Fproducts, are available to pre-order
OL,20,Ffrom Friday.
